snippet.title: WWE - Road to Wrestlemania X8 - GBA
snippet.description:
Watch me masterfully win a Royal Rumble match :-)

WWE Road to WrestleMania X8 is a video game released on the Game Boy Advance handheld console by THQ, based on WWE's pay-per-view of the same name. It featured improved gameplay and grappling technics to its predecessor. This game was the successor to WWF Road to WrestleMania. The game was succeeded by WWE Survivor Series. 

See this page for a control guide...
http://www.gamefaqs.com/gba/561492-wwe-road-to-wrestlemania-x8/faqs/20197
